data.description: This remodeled 2 bed, 2 bath home in within walking distance of the town sq. When you sit on the back patio or relax in the hot tube, you can view 40 + acres of undeveloped land right behind your property. Real hardwood floors throughout the house. Like to cook? Marble countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas stovetop. Oversized tiled shower & bathroom. The sitting area upstairs could be turned into the 3rd bedroom. New roof, Havoc & windows makes this WALK-IN READY! Don't forget the unfinished basement (not included in the sq. footage) for storage & a huge man shed in the backyard. Plus 13 mature fruit trees This is a must-see house. Now offering One-year Simple Home Warranty Service Agreement. Look in Docs.
